- Frames reference shared elements via `<use>` tags
- **50-90% file size reduction** compared to naive frame sequences

**Example:**
- 100-frame animation with static background
- Naive approach: 100√ó background duplication = ~5MB
- FBF.SVG: 1√ó background + frame differences = ~500KB

**Benefits:**
